==============================================================================
                     R E Q U I R E D   L I B R A R I E S
==============================================================================

MANDATORY:

   - libpcap >= 0.8.1
   - libnet  >= 1.1.1  (1.1.2 for uncofigured interfaces)
   - libpthread
   - zlib

OPTIONAL:

   To enable plugins:
      - libltdl (part of libtool)

   To have perl regexp in the filters:
      - libpcre

   To support SSH and SSL decryption:
      - openssl 0.9.7

   For the cursed GUI:
      - ncurses >= 5.3

   For the GTK+ GUI:
      - pkgconfig 0.15.0
      - Glib 2.2.2
      - Gtk+ 2.2.2
      - Atk 1.2.4
      - Pango 1.2.3




